<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Verification Approved!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{displayName}},</p>
      
      <p>Great news! We're pleased to inform you that <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> has been successfully verified on PayNow.</p>
      
      <div class="badge">✓ Verified Merchant</div>
      
      <p>Your customers will now see a verification badge on your payment pages, which helps build trust and confidence in your business.</p>
      
      <p>Benefits of being verified:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Increased customer trust and confidence</li>
        <li>Higher conversion rates on payment pages</li>
        <li>Priority customer support</li>
        <li>Access to advanced payment features</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>You can now create payment links and start accepting payments with your verified status displayed.</p>
      
      <a href="https://paynow.com/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing PayNow for your payment needs!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The PayNow Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2023 PayNow. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply to this message.</p>
    </div>
